    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior has some visible clear coat peeling and a few minor dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need a tune-up and some suspension work in the near future to keep it at its best. It's a dependable car that reflects its age and mileage honestly.",
