    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it's been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and there isn't a single blemish to be found. It drives like a total dream, and I've been super meticulous with the upkeep. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership price tag, you've found it! Come say hi and take a look!",
