    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is a superlative example of the E46 M3, maintained to an exacting standard. The S54 high-revving straight-six engine delivers linear power with no evidence of rod bearing wear, and the double-VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Besian components for peak variable valve timing precision. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement already completed. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 420G manual gearbox to a tight factory limited-slip differential. The suspension features refreshed bushings and dampers, preserving the original kinematic excellence of the M-chassis. Presented in showroom condition with zero paint imperfections and a pristine cabin, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of analog driver engagement.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
